data.title: William Kennon Sr., former Representative for Ohio's 11th Congressional District
data.meta_description: Legislative profile for Rep. William Kennon Sr. [J-OH11, 1835-1837], the former Representative from Ohio
data.text:
Kennon was the representative for Ohio’s 11th congressional district and was a Jackson. He served from 1835 to 1837.

He was previously the representative for Ohio’s 10th congressional district as a Jackson from Dec 5, 1831 to Mar 3, 1833; and the representative for Ohio’s 10th congressional district as a Jackson from Dec 7, 1829 to Mar 3, 1831.
